  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of especial diet therapy
      &quot;Anti-inflammatory Diet&quot; on inflammatory, oxidative stress, and nutritional markers in the
      context of protein-energy wasting syndrome(PEW) in hemodialysis patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
